reviewText:
You get what you pay for.  The video appears to be from a standard camcorder, the sound quality is atrocious, and the physical tapes might be the cheapest-quality I have ever run across.  Our 4-year old son has been  watching them for about 3 weeks; 1 tape is completely unusable, another is  well on its way.  I strongly recommend AGAINST the purchase of this tape  set, or any tape produced by this same organization.
Regretfully,
